      <esp:h>About</esp:h>

      <p>PCSL is the font for <esp:link
      url="http://oracc.org/pcsl">the PCSL project</esp:link>.</p>
      
      <esp:h>Original Font</esp:h>

      <p>PCSL is based on a fontification of Bob Englund's PC signs on
      github done by Anshuman Pandey.  It has been revised and
      augmented by Steve Tinney.</p>
	
      <esp:h>License</esp:h>

      <p>The PCSL font is licensed under the SIL Open Font License,
      Version 1.1.</p>

      <esp:h>Download</esp:h>

      <p>All of the Oracc fonts are downloadable from the <esp:link
      url="https://github.com/oracc/oracc2">Oracc II GitHub
      repository</esp:link> in the msc/fonts subdirectory.</p>
      
